description	"Boba Fett 

A versatile Jetpack gunner with an arsenal of Mandalorian abilities.

^2Weaponry:
- Melee
- EE-3 Carbine Rifle (3)
- FWG-5 Flechette Pistol (Shotgun 2)
-- Fires focused blasts while hovering
-- 10% less FP Dmg
-- 40% slower Mag Reload
- Wrist Rockets (5) (Conc Rifle 3)
-- Staggers/pushes on det
-- 75% less Velocity
-- 40% slower Mag Reload
- Sonic Detonator (1)
- Frag Grenades (2)

^8Attributes:
- Beskar (2)
- Blast Armor
- Healing (2)
- Tracking Beacon

^3Abilities:
- Jetpack
- Rocket ^3[CS1]
- Wrist Flamethrower ^3[CS2]
- Wrist Laser ^3[CS3]
- Whistling Birds ^3[CS4]"